You were faking it? That's pretty funny.

550
01:20:12.707 --> 01:20:14.038
Did you do your homework yet?

551
01:20:14.476 --> 01:20:16.376
I forgot. It's due first period too.

552
01:20:21.216 --> 01:20:22.240
Help me!

553
01:20:23.251 --> 01:20:25.185
Hey... Vichien is drowning.

554
01:20:25.654 --> 01:20:26.678
Help me!

555
01:20:30.392 --> 01:20:32.019
Go ahead and save him.

556
01:20:32.727 --> 01:20:33.989
But he could be faking it.

557
01:20:37.332 --> 01:20:38.424
Help me!

558
01:20:53.248 --> 01:20:54.510
Help me!

559
01:20:56.852 --> 01:20:59.082
Hey. it's 6 p.m. Let's head back.

560
01:21:12.000 --> 01:21:13.558
Let's go.

561
01:21:19.474 --> 01:21:20.771
Hey. I'm leaving now.

562
01:21:41.496 --> 01:21:44.693
Then how come they say that...

563
01:21:45.000 --> 01:21:47.434
Miss Pranee was related to your death?

564
01:21:52.340 --> 01:21:54.433
You read that newspaper. right?

565
01:22:02.550 --> 01:22:04.245
It's about my father.

566
01:22:05.020 --> 01:22:07.250
Miss Pranee didn't want me to find out.

567
01:22:12.360 --> 01:22:13.190
Vichien!

568
01:22:14.863 --> 01:22:15.887
What are you doing?

569
01:22:16.965 --> 01:22:18.227
Who gave you permission to enter?

570
01:22:18.767 --> 01:22:19.734
Come here.

571
01:22:20.235 --> 01:22:23.261
Why did you do this? Why?

572
01:22:28.143 --> 01:22:30.077
I'll hit you until I break your hand.

573
01:22:34.149 --> 01:22:36.276
I just wanted to read the news about my father.

574
01:22:41.256 --> 01:22:44.316
Unfortunately. Miss Pranee caught me first.

575
01:22:46.795 --> 01:22:49.320
Miss Pranee. Vichien hasn't
returned to the dorm yet.

576
01:23:24.232 --> 01:23:26.325
Before my accident...

577
01:23:27.168 --> 01:23:30.069
I managed to sneak back
in to steal the newspaper.

578
01:23:40.015 --> 01:23:41.448
Ever since then...

579
01:23:42.550 --> 01:23:45.451
Miss Pranee has thought that my death...

580
01:23:46.221 --> 01:23:47.483
was her fault.

581
01:24:03.972 --> 01:24:06.031
But how come you have to drown...

582
01:24:06.775 --> 01:24:08.572
over and over like this?

583
01:24:10.612 --> 01:24:11.579
I don't know.

584
01:24:13.481 --> 01:24:16.575
How much longer will you be stuck like this?

585
01:24:18.053 --> 01:24:19.418
I don't know myself.

586
01:24:21.289 --> 01:24:25.055
But it's really cold at the bottom.

587
01:24:56.458 --> 01:24:58.949
See... didn't I tell you...

588
01:24:59.594 --> 01:25:03.655
that it must be the boy who drowned in the pool.

589
01:25:05.400 --> 01:25:08.528
I've seen ghosts like this before.

590
01:25:11.473 --> 01:25:12.997
At my old house...

591
01:25:13.708 --> 01:25:17.303
a motorcycle crashed
rounding the corner one night.

592
01:25:23.651 --> 01:25:27.018
The driver flew off his bike and died instantly.

593
01:25:28.656 --> 01:25:29.850
After that...

594
01:25:30.725 --> 01:25:33.523
I'd hear the same motorbike...

595
01:25:33.761 --> 01:25:36.321
skid around the corner almost every night.

596
01:26:13.168 --> 01:26:17.195
As if the spirit hadn't been reborn yet...

597
01:26:17.705 --> 01:26:19.366
so it had to re-enact it's death...

598
01:26:19.741 --> 01:26:23.575
over and over.

599
01:26:43.031 --> 01:26:43.895
What then?

600
01:26:44.799 --> 01:26:46.699
We moved the heck out of there.

601
01:26:47.368 --> 01:26:48.562
No...

602
01:26:48.870 --> 01:26:50.770
How do we help the spirits get reborn...

603
01:26:50.838 --> 01:26:52.169
so they stop re-enacting their own deaths?

604
01:26:53.141 --> 01:26:57.373
Ghosts and humans occupy separate worlds.

605
01:26:58.246 --> 01:27:00.612
To help a ghost you must be a ghost.

606
01:27:01.916 --> 01:27:04.180
To be a ghost. you have to die first.

607
01:27:04.986 --> 01:27:08.820
Unless you can split your spirit from your body.

608
01:28:17.558 --> 01:28:18.422
Are you crazy?

609
01:28:18.926 --> 01:28:20.791
Why would you want to die?

610
01:28:25.133 --> 01:28:25.792
Ton...

611
01:28:26.634 --> 01:28:28.465
swear that you won't do it.

612
01:28:35.310 --> 01:28:37.278
Hey. promise me.

613
01:28:41.316 --> 01:28:43.216
Dr. Nui. what the hell are you looking at?

614
01:28:44.752 --> 01:28:46.549
Something's wrong with Chatree.

615
01:28:47.188 --> 01:28:48.177
He seems strange.

616
01:28:49.791 --> 01:28:51.622
Shit. the other day you said he wasn't strange.

617
01:28:52.593 --> 01:28:53.423
I know.

618
01:28:55.163 --> 01:28:58.462
But today he seems strange.

619
01:28:59.267 --> 01:29:00.131
Maybe...

620
01:29:00.568 --> 01:29:02.229
he's going to jump off the building.

621
01:29:03.404 --> 01:29:05.998
How the hell can he jump through the grille?

622
01:29:15.083 --> 01:29:16.448
Can you see that water tank?

623
01:29:18.853 --> 01:29:20.878
I've climbed to the top before.

624
01:29:21.823 --> 01:29:23.450
The view is even nicer from up there.

625
01:29:27.195 --> 01:29:28.526
I'll take you there someday.

626
01:29:55.656 --> 01:29:58.147
Chatree has disappeared.

627
01:30:11.005 --> 01:30:12.870
Playing during dinner again?

628
01:30:13.274 --> 01:30:15.742
You'll see... I'll teach you a lesson.

629
01:30:53.347 --> 01:30:54.678
Hey. Chatree! Chatree!

630
01:30:58.419 --> 01:31:00.011
Chatree. are you okay?

631
01:31:00.154 --> 01:31:00.950
Chatree. wake up!

632
01:31:07.829 --> 01:31:08.727
Killed himself. right?

633
01:31:10.398 --> 01:31:10.989
No.

634
01:31:12.066 --> 01:31:14.101
I think he split his spirit from his body.

635
01:31:14.136 --> 01:31:15.369
What are you talking about?

636
01:31:15.404 --> 01:31:16.427
Splitting spirits from what?

637
01:31:17.171 --> 01:31:18.433
He told me himself...

638
01:31:18.940 --> 01:31:22.103
that he wanted to help his
friend that drowned in the pool.

639
01:31:23.077 --> 01:31:25.568
I suggested he could if
he split his spirit from his body.

640
01:31:38.626 --> 01:31:39.388
Trust me...

641
01:31:39.994 --> 01:31:41.484
we have to take him to the old pool.

642
01:31:43.564 --> 01:31:45.759
Miss Pranee. Chatree killed himself.

643
01:32:21.869 --> 01:32:23.564
Vichien's drowning!

644
01:32:30.411 --> 01:32:30.706
Help me!

645
01:33:07.448 --> 01:33:08.437
Here!

646
01:33:08.983 --> 01:33:09.881
What's that for?

647
01:33:10.318 --> 01:33:12.183
You idiot! To break the lock!

648
01:33:30.705 --> 01:33:31.637
What do we do now?

649
01:33:46.454 --> 01:33:48.718
You told me that no one cares about you.

650
01:33:49.757 --> 01:33:50.655
How about yourself?

651
01:33:51.359 --> 01:33:52.849
Do you care about anyone else but yourself?

652
01:34:02.637 --> 01:34:04.969
Hey... let me out!

653
01:34:49.950 --> 01:34:51.577
Are you still mad at your friends...

654
01:34:51.719 --> 01:34:53.311
for not saving you from drowning?

655
01:34:53.921 --> 01:34:54.945
No. I'm not mad anymore.

656
01:34:57.958 --> 01:34:58.617
How about you?

657
01:34:59.160 --> 01:35:00.627
Do you still want to run away from school?

658
01:35:01.696 --> 01:35:02.924
No. not anymore.

659
01:35:03.531 --> 01:35:06.500
If I did. I would run straight to Namtarn's embrace.

660
01:35:08.169 --> 01:35:10.364
Hey. hey... I know what you're thinking.

661
01:35:10.705 --> 01:35:13.196
Don't get me started! I saw
the way you looked at her. too.

662
01:35:13.441 --> 01:35:15.068
I've had my heart set on her for years.

663
01:35:16.310 --> 01:35:17.709
When will we go visit her again?

664
01:35:27.088 --> 01:35:28.715
Hey... Ton...

665
01:35:35.463 --> 01:35:36.794
I've got to leave now.

666
01:36:40.861 --> 01:36:41.828
Hey... Chatree is coming to.

667
01:36:42.763 --> 01:36:44.754
Chatree! Chatree is coming to.

668
01:36:45.266 --> 01:36:46.198
Are you okay. Chatree?

669
01:36:46.901 --> 01:36:48.892
Chatree. are you okay? Chatree...

670
01:36:49.804 --> 01:36:50.964
How are you. Chatree?

671
01:36:53.808 --> 01:36:54.909
You're fine now.

672
01:36:54.944 --> 01:36:55.967
Hey... he's come to already?

673
01:36:58.679 --> 01:37:00.772
Miss Pranee. Chatree is fine now.

674
01:37:51.398 --> 01:37:53.764
I never knew our school was this big.

675
01:37:55.369 --> 01:37:58.304
Why are you so amazed by the size of our school?

676
01:37:58.939 --> 01:38:00.304
I know from experience.

677
01:38:00.641 --> 01:38:03.041
Miss Pranee made me run
around the school before.

678
01:38:03.677 --> 01:38:05.269
Tears are falling from my eyes.

679
01:38:05.813 --> 01:38:07.542
You're the one who's going to fall.

680
01:38:08.415 --> 01:38:09.746
Okay. calm down.

681
01:38:10.551 --> 01:38:11.711
I was only kidding.

682
01:38:15.022 --> 01:38:15.989
Hey. Ton...

683
01:38:17.224 --> 01:38:19.556
why didn't you tell Miss Pranee
the truth about Vichien?

684
01:38:20.427 --> 01:38:23.294
Yeah. instead of letting us all get punished.

685
01:38:27.801 --> 01:38:29.530
I don't think she'd believe me.

686
01:38:31.772 --> 01:38:35.208
But... we all believe you.

687
01:38:35.776 --> 01:38:38.472
If you happen to see another ghost...

688
01:38:39.380 --> 01:38:41.746
feel free to consult me. okay?

689
01:38:42.283 --> 01:38:44.012
But don't consult me. okay?

690
01:38:44.985 --> 01:38:47.453
Let me be the first one to consult you then.

691
01:38:48.522 --> 01:38:50.683
Why the heck do you speak with a lisp?

692
01:39:00.367 --> 01:39:10.003
Chatree Anantpitisuk. please meet
your parents in the dorm.

693
01:39:11.211 --> 01:39:12.803
I guess I'm off.

694
01:39:15.616 --> 01:39:17.106
See you guys next year.

695
01:39:21.021 --> 01:39:21.749
Good luck. man.

696
01:39:22.089 --> 01:39:23.147
Good luck.

697
01:39:37.604 --> 01:39:40.368
Ton. take me to see the swimming pool. please!

698
01:39:40.674 --> 01:39:43.108
Be patient. Toh. Let him pack his things first.

699
01:39:43.277 --> 01:39:44.642
Okay. but then can we see it?

700
01:39:44.878 --> 01:39:45.503
Yes. dear.

701
01:39:50.684 --> 01:39:52.584
Have you been eating enough food?

702
01:39:53.721 --> 01:39:55.985
You've gotten darker.

703
01:39:56.657 --> 01:39:58.625
And lost weight as well.

704
01:39:58.660 --> 01:40:00.354
You've been playing outdoors too much. right?

705
01:40:03.998 --> 01:40:05.488
Mom. you're embarrassing me.

706
01:40:06.367 --> 01:40:07.561
Why be embarrassed?

707
01:40:07.768 --> 01:40:10.828
When you're older I won't get to hug you anymore.

708
01:40:15.209 --> 01:40:17.006
Toh. stay around here. okay.

709
01:40:18.479 --> 01:40:20.037
Let's get your bags. dear.

710
01:40:42.803 --> 01:40:43.735
Dad...

711
01:40:46.473 --> 01:40:47.804
I like this school now.

712
01:41:22.242 --> 01:41:23.072
Miss Pranee...

713
01:41:30.451 --> 01:41:32.214
Vichien didn't kill himself.

714
01:41:36.857 --> 01:41:40.793
His drowning was really an accident.

715
01:41:49.703 --> 01:41:51.330
Vichien asked me to apologize...

716
01:41:53.040 --> 01:41:55.099
for breaking your record player that day.

717
01:42:03.917 --> 01:42:04.941
He knows that...

718
01:42:06.453 --> 01:42:08.318
you were concerned about him.

719
01:42:17.831 --> 01:42:18.855
Thank you. Miss Pranee...

720
01:42:19.233 --> 01:42:20.860
for always taking care of us.

721
01:42:23.403 --> 01:42:24.495
See you next year. Miss Pranee.

722
01:43:09.449 --> 01:43:12.714
I still remember the first
day my father took me home.

723
01:43:15.822 --> 01:43:19.383
It was a Friday afternoon much like any other.

724
01:43:20.994 --> 01:43:24.293
But something had changed inside of me.

725
01:43:26.466 --> 01:43:28.730
That term. I only grew two centimeters.

726
01:43:29.736 --> 01:43:31.636
It'll be a while before I'm a grown man.

727
01:43:35.108 --> 01:43:39.135
Being friends with Vichien
has taught me many things.

728
01:43:56.163 --> 01:43:57.187
I didn't know...

729
01:43:58.732 --> 01:44:02.065
what adventures the next term had in store.

730
01:44:03.837 --> 01:44:06.533
But I knew that wanted to rejoin my gang of friends.

731
01:44:07.808 --> 01:44:11.835
Because I've learned that
with one close friend by your side...

732
01:44:12.846 --> 01:44:15.212
even the worst things in life...

733
01:44:15.882 --> 01:44:18.817
will eventually pass...

734
01:44:19.686 --> 01:44:21.620
in just one short breath.

735
01:44:22.305 --> 01:45:22.339
Do you want subtitles for any video?
-=[ ai.OpenSubtitles.com ]=-
